          with hands-on experience in building scalable web applications using
          .NET Core and RESTful APIs. Skilled in C#, Java, and PostgreSQL, with
          a strong understanding of clean code principles and design patterns
          such as Repository and Unit of Work. Passionate about backend
          development, eager to grow in Spring Boot or .NET environments. Known
          for being a fast learner, team player, and dedicated to delivering
          maintainable code.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img
        class="p-2 aspect-square max-h-[300px]"
        src="https://placehold.co/600x600"
